text: <@U02918BKW> can I request a beta invite with my uncorked email or should I request with my personal?

with the Free plan, we get full access to all parts of the software. no timeouts, no watermarks. not sure about commercial use. 5gb space, and 5 private active documents (unlimited public or private inactive documents)
Pro is $100/user/month (billed monthly or yearly), includes all Free features, plus unlimited private active documents, and unlimited space.
fine either way, let me know if its starting to tip over into commercial use
